ivardefs.name: billingCode_
ivardefs.desc: Billing code associated to the  item in the context of this  entry of the catalog.

ivardefs.name: billingSummary
ivardefs.desc: Billing summary attached to the  item in the context of this  entry of the catalog.

ivardefs.name: effectivePeriod
ivardefs.desc: Period of usability of the catalog entry.

ivardefs.name: estimatedDuration
ivardefs.desc: Estimated duration of the orderable item of this  entry of the catalog.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Business identifier uniquely assigned to the catalog entry.

ivardefs.name: limitationSummary
ivardefs.desc: Summary of limitations for the  item in the context of this  entry of the catalog.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: The name of this catalog entry announces the item that is represented by the entry.

ivardefs.name: note_
ivardefs.desc: Notes and comments about this catalog entry.

ivardefs.name: orderable
ivardefs.desc: Indicates whether or not the entry represents an item that is orderable.

ivardefs.name: referencedItem
ivardefs.desc: The item (resource) that this entry of the catalog represents.

ivardefs.name: regulatorySummary
ivardefs.desc: Regulatory summary for the  item in the context of this  entry of the catalog.

ivardefs.name: relatedEntry_
ivardefs.desc: Used for example, to point to a substance, or to a device used to administer a medication.

ivardefs.name: scheduleSummary
ivardefs.desc: Schedule summary for the  item in the context of this  entry of the catalog.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: Indicates whether this catalog entry is open to public usage (active) or not (draft or retired).

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: The type of resource that is represented by this catalog entry.

ivardefs.name: updatedBy
ivardefs.desc: Last actor who recorded (created or updated) this catalog entry.

properties.desc: Catalog entries are wrappers that contextualize items included in a catalog.
